# Keep Plan Files

- Every plan produced during development must be copied to `docs/plans/` with a date prefix (e.g. `2026-06-12-goldenmcp-eval-marketplace.md`).
- Never delete or overwrite plan files; append revisions as new dated files.
- README must link to `docs/plans/` for judge review.
